gobblin.broker.iface

Interface SubscopedBrokerBuilder<S extends ScopeType<S>,B extends SharedResourcesBroker<S>>


  • public interface SubscopedBrokerBuilder<S extends ScopeType<S>,B extends SharedResourcesBroker<S>>
    A builder used to create new SharedResourcesBroker compatible with an existing SharedResourcesBroker (i.e. guaranteeing objects are correctly shared among scopes).

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      B build()

      Specify additional ancestor SharedResourcesBroker.

    • Method Detail

      • withAdditionalParentBroker

        SubscopedBrokerBuilder<S,B> withAdditionalParentBroker(SharedResourcesBroker<S> broker)
        Specify additional ancestor SharedResourcesBroker. Useful when a ScopeType has multiple parents.

      • withOverridingConfig

        SubscopedBrokerBuilder<S,B> withOverridingConfig(Config config)
        Specify Config overrides. Note these overrides will only be applicable at the new leaf scope and descendant scopes. Config entries must start with BrokerConstants.GOBBLIN_BROKER_CONFIG_PREFIX (any entries not satisfying that condition will be ignored).

      • build

        B build()
        Returns:
        the new SharedResourcesBroker.
